# Patient Workflow

## Reception (all patients)

1. Register patient → unique `Patient ID`
2. Classify: civilian | military (+ rank for military)
3. Link `ContractCompany`
4. Issue **Dynamic QR** on patient card
5. Self-service: patient scans QR for queue position and ETA

## Civilian path (`PATH_STANDARD`)

| Stage | Action |
|-------|--------|
| Reception + exam | Doctor diagnosis on system |
| Technical spec | Technician enters item codes/qty only — **no prices, no stock qty** visible |
| Auto pricing | Background engine: **Highest Purchase Price** per item + margin |
| Quote | Official quote PDF with QR; wait for contract approval |
| Approval scan | Scan quote QR + upload approval letter → auto route to operations |
| Warehouse | Barcode dispense against work order; deduct stock |
| Delivery | Fitting → final QR scan → close case + invoice to contract entity |

## Military path (`PATH_MILITARY`)

Same through technical spec; then:

- Silent cost calculation in background (no quote, no payment hold)
- Auto skip to **ready for production** after pricing event
- Delivery closes case; cost posts to **sovereign debt** aggregate — not patient billing

## `CaseRecord` stage keys (source of truth)

`reception` → `exam` → `technical` → `cost_calc` → `admin_approval` → `quote` → `waiting_return` → `manufacturing` → `delivered`

Manufacturing sub-stages: `warehouse`, `workshop`, `fitting`, `quality`, `issue`, `generation`, `assembly`, `casting`, `finishing`, `closed`

## Event-driven transitions (implement in Service, not UI)

| Trigger | Transition |
|---------|------------|
| Doctor approves exam | → awaiting technical spec |
| Spec saved | → auto pricing |
| Pricing done (civilian) | → awaiting contract approval |
| Pricing done (military) | → ready for production |
| Approval QR scanned (civilian) | → ready for production + work order no |
| Barcode dispense confirmed | → under manufacturing |
| Production complete | → ready for delivery |
| Delivery QR scan | → **closed** + financial posting |

Never add manual stage-change endpoints without a domain event.
